    "attributes": {
        "action": "National guidelines to standardise burial fees and ban non-resident surcharges ",
        "additional_details": "We call on the Government to issue guidance to local authorities to make burial fees fair and consistent. Families already grieving face a postcode lottery. It is especially unfair when lifelong residents who move boroughs for care are charged more. At such a difficult time, people deserve dignity, fairness, and compassion.",
        "background": "We want the Government to issue national guidance to local authorities to ensure fair and consistent burial charges across the country and remove \u201cnon-resident\u201d surcharges.",
